ikaze-kimiko-and-correspondence-of-nintendo-and-youtube/embed/#?secret=06hZIoT9Ni#?secret=AxThqMxASm" data-secret="AxThqMxASm" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>这次，在与 Kenki 的广播中，曾根 Tomeru 多次发表了有关《AV Splatoon》的言论。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="AV Splatoon VTuber的例子真实到让人发笑[Kenki剪辑]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u2q4LTJgLOg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="xnnmt653ddc4130f81" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
